      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know, but i cant really get to a doctor right now since it's the weekend and my clinic is closed. i've taken ibuprofen for headaches a lot in the past and it's always worked fine. is the risk really that high if i just take one or two tablets? it's getting pretty hard to think straight.",
